<a href="http://www.justdave.net/dave/">Dave Miller</a>, is sysadmin for the <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/">Mozilla project</a> running a few thousand servers,
during the official work hours, and leading the <a href="http://www.bugzilla.org/">Bugzilla</a> project in his little spare time.

He learned Perl by hacking on Bugzilla more than 10 years ago.

